channel.title: ChefScape Developement :)
channel.description:
Ok well guys I'm working on a really cool server called ChefScape so I think I'm supposed to post it here. :)
OK. So first let me list what the server will have at finish time.
[ul][li]100% Bug-Free Trading[/li] [li]Lots of custom items![/li] [li]Cool custom item special attacks![/li] [li]Almost 100% Bounty Hunter (collecting the map data + sprites)[/li] [li]Almost 100% Grand Exchange (just need interfaces)[/li] [li]Almost 100% Dueling :S (I need some things to work better.)[/li] [li]Pretty cool home, spread out.[/li] [li][b]MY FAVORITE THING:[/b] GREAT PERFORMANCE! The server is based off of the highly efficent and stable WinterLove! :D[/li] [li]Practically no bugs. I added something called an anti-cheat hack client detecter. When you do ::noclip it tells everyone that he is no clipping and reports.[/li] [li]No crappy emote teleports. -.- thats dumb.[/li] [li]Almost 100% for all skills! (exept summoning, construction and hunter :() [/li][li]An awsome client backround + login screen. :rolleyes:[/li] [li]A COOOOLL Mini-Game called Banana Monster Hunt that I made. ;)[/li] [li]And when hosting the server will be hosted off RSMedival's free VPS service. ;D[/li][/ul]
Ok so I can add pictures later... but if you think I'm lying about some stuff I made these videos in the morning. (I have to go to the mall right now)
[url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Yz4ppZMMFYQ]Grand Exchange Video[/url] [url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2SAK-MX32Jo]Dueling Video[/url]
Ok so tell me what you like and what you don't like. I probably will realease in the next week or so :cool:
